CAASATURNPlanet

CAASATURNPlanet.Rd

CAASATURNPlanet

CAASATURNPlanet(Year)

Arguments

Year

Year The year. (Years are counted astronomically i.e. 1 BC = Year 0)

Details

Value

A list containing the astronomical phenomena for Saturn.

References

Author

C++ code by PJ Naughter, imported to R by Jinlong Zhang
